{"pageProps":{"post":{"title":"集合と関係","date":"2021-08-13T20:35:07","slug":"二項関係","content":"<h2>集合の演算</h2>\n<h3>冪集合 power set</h3>\n<p><span><span><span>AA</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>A</span></span></span></span></span> の部分集合をすべて集めた集合である。</p>\n<p><span><span><span>2A2^A</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span><span>2</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>A</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> などと表記する。</p>\n<p>すなわち、</p>\n<div><span><span><span>∀x.(x∈2A⇔x⊂A)\\forall x. (x \\in 2^A \\Leftrightarrow x \\subset A)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>∀</span><span>x</span><span>.</span><span>(</span><span>x</span><span></span><span>∈</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>2</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>A</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span>⇔</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>x</span><span></span><span>⊂</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>A</span><span>)</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<p>が成立する。</p>\n<p><span><span><span>A={a,b,c}A = \\{a,b,c\\}</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>=</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>{</span><span>a</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>b</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>c</span><span>}</span></span></span></span></span>とすると、</p>\n<div><span><span><span>2A={ϕ,{a},{b},{c},{a,b},{b,c},{c,a},{a,b,c}}2^A = \\{\\phi, \\{a\\}, \\{b\\}, \\{c\\}, \\{a,b\\}, \\{b,c\\}, \\{c,a\\}, \\{a,b,c\\}\\}</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span><span>2</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>A</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span>=</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>{</span><span>ϕ</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>{</span><span>a</span><span>}</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>{</span><span>b</span><span>}</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>{</span><span>c</span><span>}</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>{</span><span>a</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>b</span><span>}</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>{</span><span>b</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>c</span><span>}</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>{</span><span>c</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>a</span><span>}</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>{</span><span>a</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>b</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>c</span><span>}</span><span>}</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<h3>和集合 union</h3>\n<p><span><span><span>AA</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>A</span></span></span></span></span>と<span><span><span>BB</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>B</span></span></span></span></span>の和集合は<span><span><span>A∪BA\\cup B</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>∪</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>B</span></span></span></span></span>と表し、</p>\n<div><span><span><span>∀x.(x∈A∪B⇔(x∈A∨x∈B))\\forall x. (x \\in A \\cup B \\Leftrightarrow (x \\in A \\lor x \\in B))</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>∀</span><span>x</span><span>.</span><span>(</span><span>x</span><span></span><span>∈</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>∪</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>B</span><span></span><span>⇔</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>(</span><span>x</span><span></span><span>∈</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>∨</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>x</span><span></span><span>∈</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>B</span><span>)</span><span>)</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<p>を満たす。</p>\n<h3>積集合（共通部分） intersection</h3>\n<p>交叉ともいう。</p>\n<p>積集合というと直積集合の意味で用いられることも多い。</p>\n<p><span><span><span>AA</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>A</span></span></span></span></span>と<span><span><span>BB</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>B</span></span></span></span></span>の共通部分は<span><span><span>A∩BA\\cap B</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>∩</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>B</span></span></span></span></span>と表し、</p>\n<div><span><span><span>∀x.(x∈A∪B⇔(x∈A∧x∈B))\\forall x. (x \\in A \\cup B \\Leftrightarrow (x \\in A \\land x \\in B))</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>∀</span><span>x</span><span>.</span><span>(</span><span>x</span><span></span><span>∈</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>∪</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>B</span><span></span><span>⇔</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>(</span><span>x</span><span></span><span>∈</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>∧</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>x</span><span></span><span>∈</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>B</span><span>)</span><span>)</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<p>を満たす。</p>\n<h3>差集合 set difference</h3>\n<p>集合<span><span><span>AA</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>A</span></span></span></span></span>と<span><span><span>BB</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>B</span></span></span></span></span>の差集合を<span><span><span>A−BA-B</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>−</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>B</span></span></span></span></span>と表し、</p>\n<div><span><span><span>∀x.(x∈A−B⇔(x∈A∧x∉B))\\forall x. (x \\in A-B \\Leftrightarrow (x \\in A \\land x \\notin B))</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>∀</span><span>x</span><span>.</span><span>(</span><span>x</span><span></span><span>∈</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>−</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>B</span><span></span><span>⇔</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>(</span><span>x</span><span></span><span>∈</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>∧</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>x</span><span></span><span><span><span>∈</span></span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span><span>/</span><span></span></span></span><span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>B</span><span>)</span><span>)</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<p>を満たす。</p>\n<h3>直積集合 cartesian product</h3>\n<p>集合<span><span><span>AA</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>A</span></span></span></span></span>と<span><span><span>BB</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>B</span></span></span></span></span>の直積集合を<span><span><span>A×BA \\times B</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>×</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>B</span></span></span></span></span>と表し、</p>\n<div><span><span><span>A×B={(a,b)∣a∈A∧b∈B}A \\times B = \\{(a,b) | a\\in A \\land b \\in B\\}</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>×</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>B</span><span></span><span>=</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>{</span><span>(</span><span>a</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>b</span><span>)</span><span>∣</span><span>a</span><span></span><span>∈</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>∧</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>b</span><span></span><span>∈</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>B</span><span>}</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<p>である。</p>\n<p>※ <span><span><span>(a,b)(a,b)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>(</span><span>a</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>b</span><span>)</span></span></span></span></span>はタプル</p>\n<p>一般に可換ではなく、<span><span><span>A×B≠B×AA \\times B \\ne B \\times A</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>×</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>B</span><span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span></span></span><span></span></span></span></span></span><span>=</span></span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>B</span><span></span><span>×</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>A</span></span></span></span></span>である。</p>\n<h2>関係とは？</h2>\n<p><span><span><span>A1,A2,⋯ ,AnA_1, A_2, \\cdots, A_n</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span><span>A</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>1</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span>,</span><span></span><span><span>A</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>2</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span>,</span><span></span><span>⋯</span><span></span><span></span><span>,</span><span></span><span><span>A</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>n</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> を集合とするとき、<span><span><span>A1×A2×⋯AnA_1 \\times A_2 \\times \\cdots A_n</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span><span>A</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>1</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span>×</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>A</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>2</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span>×</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>⋯</span><span></span><span><span>A</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>n</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>の部分集合\nを <span><span><span>A1,A2,⋯ ,AnA_1, A_2, \\cdots, A_n</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span><span>A</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>1</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span>,</span><span></span><span><span>A</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>2</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span>,</span><span></span><span>⋯</span><span></span><span></span><span>,</span><span></span><span><span>A</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>n</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 上の <span><span><span>nn</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>n</span></span></span></span></span>項関係という。</p>\n<p><span><span><span>RR</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>R</span></span></span></span></span>が<span><span><span>A1,A2,⋯ ,AnA_1, A_2, \\cdots, A_n</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span><span>A</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>1</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span>,</span><span></span><span><span>A</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>2</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span>,</span><span></span><span>⋯</span><span></span><span></span><span>,</span><span></span><span><span>A</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>n</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>上の<span><span><span>nn</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>n</span></span></span></span></span>項関係であるとは、</p>\n<div><span><span><span>R⊂A1×A2×⋯×AnR \\subset A_1 \\times A_2 \\times \\cdots \\times A_n</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>R</span><span></span><span>⊂</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>A</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>1</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span>×</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>A</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>2</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span>×</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>⋯</span><span></span><span>×</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>A</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>n</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<p>をいう。</p>\n<p>特に、<span><span><span>n=2n=2</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>n</span><span></span><span>=</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>2</span></span></span></span></span>のときの関係を二項関係という。</p>\n<p><span><span><span>RR</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>R</span></span></span></span></span>が二項関係のとき、<span><span><span>(x,y)∈R(x,y) \\in R</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>(</span><span>x</span><span>,</span><span></span><span>y</span><span>)</span><span></span><span>∈</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>R</span></span></span></span></span> を <span><span><span>xRyxRy</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>x</span><span>R</span><span>y</span></span></span></span></span>とも書く。</p>\n<h2>二項関係</h2>\n<p><span><span><span>RR</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>R</span></span></span></span></span> を集合<span><span><span>AA</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>A</span></span></span></span></span>上の二項関係、すなわち<span><span><span>R⊂A×AR \\subset A \\times A</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>R</span><span></span><span>⊂</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>A</span><span></span><span>×</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>A</span></span></span></span></span> である。</p>\n<p>二項関係には以下の性質がある。</p>\n<h3>反射的 reflexive</h3>\n<div><span><span><span>∀x.(xRx)\\forall x. (xRx)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>∀</span><span>x</span><span>.</span><span>(</span><span>x</span><span>R</span><span>x</span><span>)</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<h3>対称的 symmetric</h3>\n<div><span><span><span>∀x∀y.(xRy⇒yRx)\\forall x \\forall y. (xRy \\Rightarrow yRx)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>∀</span><span>x</span><span>∀</span><span>y</span><span>.</span><span>(</span><span>x</span><span>R</span><span>y</span><span></span><span>⇒</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>y</span><span>R</span><span>x</span><span>)</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<h3>推移的 transitive</h3>\n<div><span><span><span>∀x∀y∀z((xRy∧yRz)⇒xRz)\\forall x \\forall y \\forall z ((xRy \\land yRz) \\Rightarrow xRz)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>∀</span><span>x</span><span>∀</span><span>y</span><span>∀</span><span>z</span><span>(</span><span>(</span><span>x</span><span>R</span><span>y</span><span></span><span>∧</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>y</span><span>R</span><span>z</span><span>)</span><span></span><span>⇒</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>x</span><span>R</span><span>z</span><span>)</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<h3>反対称的 antisymmetric</h3>\n<div><span><span><span>∀x∀y((xRy∧yRx)⇒x=y)\\forall x \\forall y ((xRy \\land yRx) \\Rightarrow x = y)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>∀</span><span>x</span><span>∀</span><span>y</span><span>(</span><span>(</span><span>x</span><span>R</span><span>y</span><span></span><span>∧</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>y</span><span>R</span><span>x</span><span>)</span><span></span><span>⇒</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>x</span><span></span><span>=</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>y</span><span>)</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<h2>順序・半順序</h2>\n<p>集合<span><span><span>AA</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>A</span></span></span></span></span>上の二項関係において、反射的かつ推移的かつ反対称的であるものを\n<span><span><span>AA</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>A</span></span></span></span></span>上の半順序(partial order) という。</p>\n<p>順序<span><span><span>RR</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>R</span></span></span></span></span>で以下の条件を満たすものを全順序(total order) という。</p>\n<div><span><span><span>∀x∈A∀y∈A(xRy∨yRx)\\forall x \\in A \\forall y \\in A (xRy \\lor yRx)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>∀</span><span>x</span><span></span><span>∈</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>A</span><span>∀</span><span>y</span><span></span><span>∈</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>A</span><span>(</span><span>x</span><span>R</span><span>y</span><span></span><span>∨</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span>y</span><span>R</span><span>x</span><span>)</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<p>→ すべての2要素が比較可能</p>\n","tags":["基礎","離散数学","関係"]}},"__N_SSG":true}